io.spine.server.tuple

Class Pair<A extends com.google.protobuf.Message,B>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.server.tuple.Tuple
      • io.spine.server.tuple.Pair<A,B>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - the type of the first element
    B - the type of the second element
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<com.google.protobuf.Message>

    public final class Pair<A extends com.google.protobuf.Message,B>
extends Tuple
    A tuple with two elements.

    The first element must be a non-default Message and not Empty.

    The second element can be Message, Optional or Either.
